# Client configuration
#
# In this single-service setup, the client is served by the same origin as the API,
# so API calls can use relative paths (e.g. fetch('/health')) and no env var is required.
#
# Only set this if you run the client on a different origin than the server during development.
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:4000

# Canonical origin for SEO (public marketing pages) — used to build absolute
# canonical + OG URLs only. Does NOT affect any functional link (those derive
# from PUBLIC_ORIGIN on the server or window.location.origin on the client).
# Set at build time to the public marketing domain; unset falls back to the
# literal in src/public/seo/siteMeta.js.
# VITE_PUBLIC_BASE_URL=https://www.grafitiyul.co.il
